Repeat: purl wrapping yarn twice around needle for each stitch

sl 4 wyib dropping extra wraps then insert left-hand needle into 1st and 2nd stitches, pass them over 3rd and 4th stitches and onto left-hand needle like a psso; then slip remaining 2 stitches also back onto left-hand needle in position to be knitted first, then knit all 4 stitches
